properties.name: OMN - YEM
properties.comment: Although it's possible to fly in to Yemen (especially to Soccotra), land borders remain closed.
The land borders of Azerbaijan have been closed to tourists since COVID.

THA - KHM
properties.comment: The Border has been closed since the 2025 skirmishes between the 2 armies.

properties.name: PAN - COL
properties.comment:
There is no road between Panama and Colombia. In fact, the area is thick jungle, and is only crossed illegally on foot.
The only option is to fly or ship its vehicle between the two countries.
The border is closed, except for pilgrims heading to Mecca.

YEM - SAU
properties.comment: Although it's possible to fly in to Yemen (especially to Soccotra), land borders remain closed - although there are unconfirmed reports of people crossing at Although it's possible to fly in to Yemen (especially to Soccotra), land borders at Al Wadiyah into a region which is mostly stable. But getting a visa in next to impossible.

properties.name: ARM - AZE
properties.comment:
The border has been reshaped after the 2020 war which saw Azerabijan regaining full control over Nagorno Karakbagh. 
It has been closed since the first war between the two countries and there is little hope to see it reopen.

properties.name: SAH - MAR
properties.comment: This is not a wall-defined border, it's just the eastern limit until the the Moroccans control the country. Do not get close, there are often skirmishes with Polisario fighters.

properties.name: TUR - ARM
properties.comment:
The border has always been closed, due to the very bad relationships between Turkey and Armenia, related to the Armenian genocide.
There are no plan to re-open it in the near or long future.

properties.name: MAR - DZA
properties.comment: The border with Morocco and Algeria has been closed for all traffic since 1994 and the Algerian civil war.
All land borders of Azerbaijan are closed to tourists since COVID.

properties.comment: There is only one border crossing between Georgia and Russia, along the Georgian Military Road.
